  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In the proposed project the investigators will develop and test a novel brief intervention
      targeting college students who drink heavily to cope with anxiety and depression, a behavior
      that increases risk for the development of alcohol dependence.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
